  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "chapterTitle": "第一章 绪论：政府行为与中央—地方关系",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300053174_21_4411-4471",
          "range": "4411-4471",
          "rangeStart": 4411,
          "rangeEnd": 4471,
          "markText": "到底是以市场化改革促发展，还是以政府调节实现社会平等和经济增长，在意识形态方面就表现为所谓“右派”和“左派”的激烈争论。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1699345615,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-11-07 16:26:55",
          "chapterUid": 21,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053174&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=4411&rangeEnd=4471",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326a0813ab7b45g014524?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=4411&rangeEnd=4471"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300053174_21_4226-4332",
          "range": "4226-4332",
          "rangeStart": 4226,
          "rangeEnd": 4332,
          "markText": "这种控制和动员能力是改革前计划经济体制的产物，和改革后市场经济的发展存在着明显的矛盾。市场转型要求政府放权，但是政府要保持其强大的推动经济增长、调节社会分配以及其他方面的能力，则必然要求拥有全面的主导和控制能力。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1699345615,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-11-07 16:26:55",
          "chapterUid": 21,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053174&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=4226&rangeEnd=4332",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326a0813ab7b45g014524?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=4226&rangeEnd=4332"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300053174_21_2033-2069",
          "range": "2033-2069",
          "rangeStart": 2033,
          "rangeEnd": 2069,
          "markText": "中央和地方基本走出了改革开放前高度集权的局面，形成了财政分权的初步格局。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1699345614,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-11-07 16:26:54",
          "chapterUid": 21,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053174&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2033&rangeEnd=2069",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326a0813ab7b45g014524?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2033&rangeEnd=2069"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300053174_21_9372-9414",
          "range": "9372-9414",
          "rangeStart": 9372,
          "rangeEnd": 9414,
          "markText": "到1990年代初期，地方政府已经成为独立的利益主体，并且对中央政府的控制构成了挑战。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1699345614,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-11-07 16:26:54",
          "chapterUid": 21,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053174&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=9372&rangeEnd=9414",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326a0813ab7b45g014524?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=9372&rangeEnd=9414"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300053174_21_3526-3583",
          "range": "3526-3583",
          "rangeStart": 3526,
          "rangeEnd": 3583,
          "markText": "中央政府看来，经济发展是社会稳定的前提，而在地方政府看来，经济增长既符合中央政府的设定目标，更符合自身的主体利益，",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1699345613,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-11-07 16:26:53",
          "chapterUid": 21,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053174&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=3526&rangeEnd=3583",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326a0813ab7b45g014524?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=3526&rangeEnd=3583"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300053174_21_1501-1534",
          "range": "1501-1534",
          "rangeStart": 1501,
          "rangeEnd": 1534,
          "markText": "在包干制下，地方政府逐渐成为了追求地方经济和财政收入增长的利益主体",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1699345612,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-11-07 16:26:52",
          "chapterUid": 21,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053174&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=1501&rangeEnd=1534",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326a0813ab7b45g014524?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=1501&rangeEnd=1534"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300053174_21_5932-6138",
          "range": "5932-6138",
          "rangeStart": 5932,
          "rangeEnd": 6138,
          "markText": "这个主题的研究由两种对立的假设构成，即“精英替代理论”和“精英再生产理论”。精英替代理论假设在过去的计划经济体制中掌握资源分配权力的政治精英将逐渐被市场转型过程中兴起的经济精英和社会精英所替代，或者说社会的精英集团将呈现出分化的趋势，没有一种精英团体会像过去一样全面垄断社会资源的分配权。精英再生产理论则认为旧有的政治精英会在转型过程中利用其已经掌握的权力去维持在经济和社会中的地位，成长为新的经济精英和社会精英",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1699345612,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-11-07 16:26:52",
          "chapterUid": 21,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053174&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=5932&rangeEnd=6138",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326a0813ab7b45g014524?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=5932&rangeEnd=6138"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
